aa(lp374
VLet me just show you one thing.
p375
aVI have a little acorn here
p376
aVthat I picked up while I was walking on the path earlier this year.
p377
aVNow, the acorn is associated with the oak tree, of course \u2014
p378
aVgrows into an oak tree, which is associated with Abraham.
p379
aVThe path right now is like an acorn;
p380
